wizernes_base

Wizernes_base is a remake of the map by the same name in Return to Castle Wolfenstein. The map features 32 spawn points, and a working radar file. You can play the map on the ** WOLFENSTEIN CONQUEST ** server at 205.234.203.82:27015

The map features a working nav, custom radar and some sounds.

To install, place the .bsp in your cstrike/maps folder

Download the deathmatch version from [Here](http://dl.dropbox.com/u/1491682/Winzernes/final/dm_wizernes_base.rar "dm version")
